mon Moon: Super Music Collection|There\'s Trouble!]], is used instead of the normal title card jingle.\n* [[Nanu]], [[Hala]], and [[Olivia]] narrate the preview for the [[SM089|next episode]].\n* The English dub title is reference to the 1945 song {{wp|Full Moon and Empty Arms}}.\n* In the English dub, this episode is the first to not remove all mentions of Matori\'s name.\n* The English dub of the episode was released on Amazon Video on January 19, 2019, and on the [[iTunes Store]] and [[Google Play]] on January 20, 2019, seven and six days before it aired in {{pmin|the United States}}, respectively.\n\n===Errors===\n\n===Dub edits===\n\n==In other languages==\n{{Epilang|color=90BDDC|bordercolor=F1912B\n|zh_cmn={{tt|露奈雅拉 VS. ＵＢ：漆黑！滿月之戰！！|Lunala VS UB Black! A Full Moon Battle!!}}\n|da={{tt|Fuldmåne og mange hænder!|Full moon and lots of hands!}}\n|fi={{tt|Kaiken peittävä pimeys!|The darkness that covers everything!}}\n|fr_eu={{tt|Tous unis sous la pleine lune !|All united under the full moon!}}\n|ko={{tt|루나아라 대 UB:BLACK! 보름달의 싸움!!|Lunala VS UB:BLACK! A Full Moon Battle!!}}\n|no={{tt|Fullmåne og mange armer!|Full moon and lots of arms!}}\n|pl={{tt|Wszyscy razem przy pełni księżyca!|Everyone together unter the full moon!}}\n|pt_br={{tt|A escuridão envolvente!|The involving darkness!}}\n|he={{tt|!נלחמים לאור הירח המלא|Battling Infront of the Full Moon!}}\n|es_la={{tt|¡Una oscuridad envolvente!|The enveloping darkness!}}\n|es_eu={{tt|¡Solgaleo y Lunala en peligro!|Solgaleo and Lunala in danger!}}\n|sv={{tt|Förstörelse Från Bortom Ultra Maskhålet!|Destruction From Beyond the Ultra Wormhole!}}\n|tr={{tt|Dolunay ve Silahlar!|Full Moon and Arms!}}\n|th={{tt|ลูนาอาลา ปะทะ ยูบีแบล็ค การต่อสู้ของจันทร์เต็มดวง!!|Lunala VS UB:BLACK! A Full Moon Battle!!}}\n}}\n{{-}}\n{{EpicodePrevNext|\nprevcode=SM087 |\nprevtitle=Filling the Light with Darkness! |\nnextcode=SM089 |\nnexttitle=The Prism Between Light and Darkness! |\nseries=Sun & Moon series |\ncolorscheme=Alola}}\n{{Project An